title: The Gate Busters - Club for any JG/TOP that has unlocked the secrets
body:
^Cringe asf

If you win your games and focus around the split push in general (any role really) then this is the club for you. Not only is it some trash "social gathering", it's also a strategy discussion. We already have 10 members. We will talk about new items, new metas, new builds, you will be able to get a group to play a game with, and if you play any of these champions \/ you are a goddamn legend.
